{"tid":1380904,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[武術界恥辱]空手道正德館館長公開撐警屌年青人","createTime":"2019-07-29T06:26:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-12T14:31:46.000Z","uid":293079,"like":126,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"31c6048212c478f627912b6bb02189467f492582","tid":1380904,"uid":293079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:26:16.000Z","msg":"呼籲家長集體杯葛剛柔流空手道正德館，唔好比兒女跟錯人，入錯館。<br />\n<br />\n館長公然撐警隊，更宣稱年青人冇捱過苦同夠班嗎。<br />\n<br />\n我屌你老母趙慧玲，身為習武之人，眼見平民百姓被打，警方無力，仲要撐警方？<br />\n你條仆街拖教練費唔找，不斷搵徒弟做免費勞工已經街知巷聞，成大班打得嘅學生都轉咗館！<br />\n你唔止冇武德，你簡直係侮辱空手道，侮辱習武之人嘅尊嚴。<br />\n<br />\n請各位廣傳！文宣請加入「剛柔流空手道正德館」為光顧黑名單！<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ASyHH26.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FASyHH26.png&h=5bb547cb&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SjG6qgs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSjG6qgs.png&h=c097a560&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b7567f2a4a13820ac395d370b7c2c1186021f0b7","tid":1380904,"uid":293079,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:27:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"588cc45f4735e070a5bc40583c98ed6aa647eefd","tid":1380904,"uid":293079,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:30:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fa